05:09.992 --> 05:13.227
YOU THOUGHT I'D BE MORE
COMFORTABLE WITHOUT A BRA?

05:13.295 --> 05:15.346
<i>I KNOW I AM.</i>

05:15.414 --> 05:16.097
COME ON.

05:16.165 --> 05:17.715
DOUG, COME ON.
LOOK, I TOLD YOU,

05:17.783 --> 05:19.751
I'M JUST
NOT READY YET, OK?

05:19.818 --> 05:22.286
I'M SORRY.
THAT'S JUST THE WAY I AM.

05:22.354 --> 05:24.689
YEAH, THAT'S
THE BOOK ON YOU.

05:27.125 --> 05:29.226
WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED
TO MEAN?

05:29.294 --> 05:30.762
NOTHING. IT'S JUST...
I DON'T KNOW.

05:30.830 --> 05:33.197
I JUST HEARD THAT BRA USED
TO COME OFF A LITTLE EASIER.

05:33.265 --> 05:35.467
YOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYIN'?
LIKE, BING!

05:36.602 --> 05:40.237
ARE YOU CALLING ME A-
A SLUT?

05:40.305 --> 05:43.508
NOT ME.
SPENCE AND DANNY.

05:43.576 --> 05:44.575
LIKE THEY KNOW ME.

05:44.643 --> 05:46.010
THEY KNOW
THE DeROBERTIS BROTHERS

05:46.078 --> 05:48.846
AND APPARENTLY,
SO DO YOU.

05:48.914 --> 05:50.698
YOU KNOW WHAT? THAT'S
REALLY NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

05:50.765 --> 05:52.066
OH, COME-IT IS
MY BUSINESS, CARRIE.

05:52.134 --> 05:53.367
IF YOU WON'T SLEEP
WITH ME, YOU KNOW,

05:53.435 --> 05:56.087
BUT YOU'LL SLEEP WITH HALF
THE DeROBERTIS-IS-IS.

05:57.606 --> 05:59.641
MAYBE THAT'S BECAUSE
THEY WERE SMART ENOUGH

05:59.708 --> 06:01.409
<i>TO FIGURE OUT
AFTER AN HOUR</i>

06:01.477 --> 06:04.345
THAT MY BRA OPENS
IN THE FRONT!

06:04.413 --> 06:07.248
OK, YOU WEAR A BRA THAT OPENS IN THE
FRONT, BUT YOU'RE NOT A SLUT. RIGHT.

06:07.316 --> 06:09.583
YOU KNOW WHAT?

06:09.651 --> 06:10.852
YOU BETTER BACK OFF
THE SLUT THING,

06:10.919 --> 06:11.953
OR YOU'RE GONNA
FIND YOURSELF

06:12.021 --> 06:14.856
IN THE TRUNK
OF GINO DeROBERTIS' CAR.

06:14.923 --> 06:18.059
GINO? YOU SLEPT
WITH THE UNCLE ALSO?!

06:18.127 --> 06:20.728
THEY'RE
A NICE FAMILY, OK?

06:20.795 --> 06:22.664
CARRIE, WHAT THE HELL'S
GOIN' ON HERE?!

06:22.731 --> 06:24.699
ALL RIGHT,
MAYBE I HOOKED UP

06:24.766 --> 06:27.068
WITH A LOT MORE GUYS THAN
I SHOULD'VE, ALL RIGHT?

06:27.136 --> 06:28.453
I DON'T KNOW
WHY I DID IT.

06:28.520 --> 06:32.256
MAYBE IT'S 'CAUSE MY MOM
DIED, AND MY DAD'S CRAZY.

06:32.324 --> 06:33.825
I HAD A SEPARATE
ENTRANCE TO THE HOUSE.

06:33.893 --> 06:35.293
I DON'T KNOW!

06:35.360 --> 06:37.729
THE POINT IS,

06:37.880 --> 06:40.548
I DON'T WANT TO BE
LIKE THAT ANYMORE, OK?

06:40.615 --> 06:44.252
I WANT TO BE IN A GROWN-UP
RELATIONSHIP WITH ONE GUY,

06:44.320 --> 06:47.172
AND I THINK I WANT
THAT GUY TO BE YOU.

06:47.239 --> 06:49.224
LET ME BE YOUR GROWN-UP.
COME ON, LET'S GO.

06:49.291 --> 06:52.660
NO, DOUG! COME ON!
I JUST TOLD YOU,

06:52.728 --> 06:55.730
I WANNA BE IN A GROWN-UP
RELATIONSHIP. YOU'RE NOT A GROWN-UP.

06:55.797 --> 06:57.498
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

06:57.566 --> 06:58.983
YEAH, YOU DON'T
- YOU DON'T HAVE ANY PLANS,

06:59.051 --> 07:00.585
YOU DON'T HAVE
ANY GOALS.

07:00.653 --> 07:01.735
I GOT PLANS.
I GOT LOTS OF GOALS.

07:01.803 --> 07:04.155
OH, OK. YOU DON'T
EVEN HAVE A JOB.

07:04.222 --> 07:06.890
Y- YES, I DO.

07:06.958 --> 07:08.109
WHAT?

07:08.176 --> 07:09.460
I WAS GONNA
SURPRISE YOU...

07:09.528 --> 07:10.861
TOMORROW,
AFTER MY FIRST DAY.

07:10.929 --> 07:13.897
<i>I CAN'T BELIEVE THAT'S
WHAT THIS IS ALL ABOUT!</i>

07:15.133 --> 07:17.469
WAIT.

07:17.536 --> 07:19.838
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

07:19.905 --> 07:22.206
YES, I'M SERIOUS.

07:24.242 --> 07:27.244
CARRIE,
BEFORE I MET YOU, I-

07:27.312 --> 07:29.614
I JUST LIKED HANGING OUT
AT A PIZZA PLACE,

07:29.682 --> 07:31.349
BUT NOW...

07:31.416 --> 07:33.284
I WANT MORE.

07:36.722 --> 07:38.822
MORE FOR MYSELF...

07:38.890 --> 07:41.159
MORE FOR YOU...

07:41.226 --> 07:43.494
more for us.

07:50.252 --> 07:51.919
WAIT, SO...
WHAT'S THE JOB?

07:51.987 --> 07:53.387
SHH.
OK.

07:57.709 --> 07:59.326
MMM...

07:59.394 --> 08:00.928
MMM.

08:00.996 --> 08:03.597
MORNING.
MORNING.

08:03.665 --> 08:05.666
WHATCHA THINKIN'?

08:05.734 --> 08:07.502
I'M THINKING IF I HADN'T DOWNED
ALL THOSE ZIMAS LAST NIGHT,

08:07.569 --> 08:10.238
I'D STAY IN BED
WITH YOU FOREVER.

08:12.157 --> 08:14.258
OH, MY GOD. I'M GONNA
BE LATE FOR WORK.

08:15.894 --> 08:17.561
OH, YEAH.

08:19.898 --> 08:21.132
HON?

08:21.200 --> 08:23.634
YEAH.
UM...

08:23.702 --> 08:26.070
AREN'T YOU
GONNA BE LATE, TOO?

08:26.138 --> 08:27.438
LATE FOR WHAT?

08:27.505 --> 08:28.973
FOR WORK!

08:29.041 --> 08:31.008
OH, THAT'S RIGHT.
WORK, WORK.

08:31.076 --> 08:32.693
MY NEW WORK!

08:32.760 --> 08:33.894
OH, YEAH.

08:33.962 --> 08:37.865
OK, SO, NOW THAT OUR
HORMONES AREN'T RAGING,

08:37.933 --> 08:39.967
TELL ME.
TELL YOU WHAT?

08:40.034 --> 08:41.635
WHAT YOUR NEW JOB IS.

08:41.703 --> 08:43.504
I NEVER TOLD YOU?!
NO.

08:43.572 --> 08:45.423
OH, THAT IS HILARIOUS!

08:48.794 --> 08:50.128
NOW, I GOTTA BE
HONEST WITH YOU,

08:50.195 --> 08:52.546
I HAVE BEEN
FANTASIZING ARCHITECT,

08:52.614 --> 08:54.415
'CAUSE I'VE ALWAYS HAD
A CRUSH ON MR. BRADY,

08:54.483 --> 08:57.785
BUT I'M REALISTIC,
SO- TELL ME.

08:57.853 --> 09:00.304
WELL, IT'S A GOOD JOB.
IT'S, UH,

09:00.372 --> 09:03.541
RIGHT DOWN THERE
IN THE, UH, JOB DISTRICT.

09:03.609 --> 09:05.943
JOB DISTRICT.
JUST TELL ME.

09:06.011 --> 09:10.114
I WILL TELL YOU IF YOU LET
ME GET A WORD IN EDGEWISE.

09:16.088 --> 09:18.990
OH, MY GOD. YOU DIDN'T
MAKE UP SOME FAKE JOB

09:19.058 --> 09:21.625
JUST SO THAT I WOULD
SLEEP WITH YOU, DID YOU?

09:21.693 --> 09:24.045
DID-WHAT-DID I-
MAKE UP-CARR-

09:24.112 --> 09:26.180
WOW, MY HEAD
IS SPINNING. WHOA.

09:26.247 --> 09:28.249
YOU DID, DIDN'T YOU?! NO!

09:28.317 --> 09:29.917
ALL RIGHT, SO, THEN JUST
TELL ME WHERE YOU WORK!

09:29.984 --> 09:31.068
OH, YOU WANNA TAKE
THAT TONE,

09:31.103 --> 09:33.453
YOU JUST LOST THE RIGHT
TO KNOW WHERE I WORK, OK?

09:33.521 --> 09:34.505
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

09:34.573 --> 09:37.809
WHAT AM I DOING? I'M
GETTING READY FOR MY...

09:37.876 --> 09:40.411
"FAKE JOB"...

09:40.562 --> 09:42.596
THAT I "MADE UP"!

09:44.632 --> 09:46.000
OK?

09:46.068 --> 09:49.403
JUST GIVE ME
A COMPANY NAME!

09:49.471 --> 09:51.088
OH, YOU WANT A NAME? IT'S A SMALL
BUSINESS. MAYBE YOU'VE HEARD OF IT?

09:51.156 --> 09:53.557
IT'S CALLED
SHUTTY INDUSTRIES!

09:58.413 --> 10:01.198
SHE EVER ASK THE DeROBERTIS
BOYS IF THEY HAVE JOBS?

10:01.266 --> 10:05.836
NO. BUT I GOTTA HAVE A JOB
'CAUSE I'M NOT A DeROBERTIS.

10:05.904 --> 10:08.589
DeROBERTIS.

10:08.657 --> 10:11.175
IT'S A COOL NAME.

10:11.242 --> 10:13.911
DOUG DeROBERTIS.

10:17.916 --> 10:19.650
OH, MY GOD. SHE'S
FOLLOWING ME.

10:19.718 --> 10:21.919
OH, THIS CHICK
HAS TRUST ISSUES.

10:21.986 --> 10:23.354
OK, JOB, JOB, JOB.

10:23.422 --> 10:25.623
GOTTA FIND A JOB.

10:38.854 --> 10:40.487
THAT WOULDN'T
END WELL.

10:43.292 --> 10:44.692
YEAH.

10:46.728 --> 10:48.062
DAMN IT!

11:07.532 --> 11:08.565
HEY, I, UH, HATE
TO BOTHER YOU,

11:08.633 --> 11:11.035
BUT CAN I, UH,
BORROW A UNIFORM?

11:11.103 --> 11:12.737
DO I KNOW YOU?

11:12.804 --> 11:14.822
NO. ANYWAY...

11:14.890 --> 11:16.556
EXTRA UNIFORM,
CAN I HAVE ONE?

11:16.624 --> 11:18.259
NO.

11:18.326 --> 11:20.344
PLEASE, YOU HAVE TO, MAN. MY
GIRLFRIEND'S FOLLOWING ME, OK?

11:20.412 --> 11:22.279
AND IF I DON'T CONVINCE HER THAT
I WORK HERE, I'M DEAD. PLEASE!

11:22.347 --> 11:25.732
I'M NOT GIVING MY UNIFORM
TO A TOTAL STRANGER.

11:25.800 --> 11:28.302
I'LL GIVE YOU SOME GUM.
YOU WANT SOME GUM?

11:28.370 --> 11:29.270
NO, I DON'T WANT
ANY GUM.

11:29.421 --> 11:31.172
WELL, HOW ABOUT THIS?
I GOT A COUPON.

11:31.239 --> 11:32.673
"BUY A WHOPPER, GET
THE SECOND WHOPPER FREE."

11:32.740 --> 11:34.708
SECOND WHOPPER FREE!

11:34.776 --> 11:36.977
LOOK, MAN, YOU'RE WEIRD,

11:37.045 --> 11:39.147
AND I DON'T LIKE YOU.

11:39.214 --> 11:42.216
SO, WHY DON'T YOU TAKE YOUR
COUPON AND YOUR FUNKY-ASS GUM

11:42.284 --> 11:43.917
AND GET ON OUT OF HERE?

12:02.737 --> 12:05.572
CARRIE. WHAT ARE YOU
DOIN' HERE?

12:05.640 --> 12:06.740
I FOLLOWED YOU.

12:06.808 --> 12:09.510
SO, DO YOU ACTUALLY
WORK HERE?

12:09.578 --> 12:10.695
NO, I JUST WALKED
IN THIS BUILDING

12:10.762 --> 12:13.664
AND PUT ON
SOME GUY'S SHIRT.

12:13.732 --> 12:15.900
HEY! WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOIN'?

12:15.968 --> 12:17.835
I KNOW, GUY.
I'M SORRY. UH,

12:17.903 --> 12:19.103
JUST GETTIN' DRESSED
HERE, AND, UH,

12:19.170 --> 12:20.338
I KNOW WE'RE SUPPOSED
TO GO OUT THERE

12:20.405 --> 12:22.189
AND MAKE THOSE DELIVERIES
AND STUFF, RIGHT?

12:28.480 --> 12:30.447
ALL RIGHT, WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON HERE?

12:30.515 --> 12:31.682
DOES HE WORK HERE
OR NOT?

12:31.750 --> 12:33.734
JUST TELL ME,
BECAUSE IF HE DOESN'T,

12:33.801 --> 12:35.586
I'M GONNA TWIST
HIS NIPPLES SO HARD

12:35.654 --> 12:38.055
THAT THEY POP OFF
LIKE BOTTLE CAPS!

12:41.793 --> 12:44.077
Y- YEAH-YEAH,
HE WORKS HERE.

12:44.145 --> 12:45.997
THERE YOU GO. YOU WANNA
DRAG IN OTHER WITNESSES,

12:46.064 --> 12:47.331
OR DO YOU
BELIEVE ME NOW?

12:47.399 --> 12:49.433
NO, I BELIEVE YOU.
I'M SORRY, BUT...

12:49.501 --> 12:51.201
WHY COULDN'T YOU JUST
TELL ME THIS BEFORE?

12:51.269 --> 12:52.386
