TO KEEP THINGS HOT.

12:52.453 --> 12:53.938
THAT'S HOW I PLAY IT IF
YOU GONNA RIDE WITH ME,

12:54.005 --> 12:54.939
YOU KNOW WHAT
I'M SAYIN'?

12:55.006 --> 12:56.140
ALL RIGHT,
ALL RIGHT. YES.

12:56.208 --> 12:57.675
ALL RIGHT. I GOTTA
GO TO ORIENTATION NOW.

12:57.743 --> 12:59.910
ALL RIGHT.
ALL RIGHT? ALL RIGHT.

13:05.733 --> 13:09.319
I CAN'T BELIEVE WE DIDN'T
THINK OF CARPOOLING BEFORE.

13:09.387 --> 13:10.988
I MEAN, I.P.S. IS RIGHT
ON MY WAY TO WORK,

13:11.055 --> 13:14.124
AND THEN I JUST PICK
YOU UP ON MY WAY HOME.

13:14.993 --> 13:17.411
YEAH.

13:17.479 --> 13:19.547
AND IT GIVES US ANOTHER
HALF-HOUR TOGETHER,

13:19.614 --> 13:24.368
JUST YOU, ME, AND IMUS.

13:24.436 --> 13:26.036
WHERE DO I TURN,
BABY?

13:26.104 --> 13:28.005
UH, I, UM...

13:28.073 --> 13:30.357
YOU DON'T KNOW? YOU BEEN
GOIN' THERE EVERY DAY.

13:30.425 --> 13:32.409
BUT I-I DON'T HAVE MY BEARINGS
WHEN I'M NOT DRIVING, OK?

13:32.477 --> 13:34.111
I MEAN, YOUR LEFT
IS MY RIGHT, AND-

13:34.179 --> 13:35.712
OH, WE'RE HERE.

14:06.011 --> 14:08.212
HEY, HOW'S IT GOIN'?

14:08.280 --> 14:10.348
HEY...

14:10.415 --> 14:11.849
AREN'T YOU THE GUY
WHO WORE MY SHIRT

14:11.916 --> 14:15.052
AND GAVE ME THOSE
EXPIRED COUPONS?

14:15.120 --> 14:16.920
YEAH, YEAH.
HEY, LISTEN,

14:16.988 --> 14:19.390
IS THERE A MULTIPLEX AROUND
HERE OR A BATTING CAGE?

14:19.458 --> 14:21.892
'CAUSE I GOTTA KILL
ABOUT 8 HOURS.

14:21.960 --> 14:23.593
WHAT'S YOUR STORY, MAN?

14:23.661 --> 14:26.347
I STARTED DATING THIS NEW
GIRL. CARRIE. YOU MET HER.

14:26.414 --> 14:27.932
OH, THE SCARY CHICK,
LOTS OF MASCARA?

14:27.999 --> 14:29.700
YEAH. SHE'S GREAT,
SHE'S GREAT.

14:29.768 --> 14:31.902
ANYWAY, I TOLD HER I HAD A JOB
SO SHE'D SLEEP WITH ME,

14:31.970 --> 14:33.336
SO I'VE BEEN PRETENDING
TO GO TO WORK EVERY DAY,

14:33.404 --> 14:34.939
BUT SUDDENLY SHE WANTS
TO CARPOOL, SO IT'S, LIKE,

14:35.006 --> 14:37.240
I ACTUALLY HAVE TO
COME HERE NOW, YOU KNOW?

14:37.308 --> 14:39.943
SOUNDS LIKE YOU KIDS
ARE GONNA MAKE IT.

14:40.011 --> 14:41.378
AND TOSS ME THAT BOX
OVER THERE, WOULD YOU?

14:41.446 --> 14:44.265
OH, YEAH, SURE.
NO PROBLEM.

14:44.332 --> 14:45.283
THIS GIRLFRIEND
OF YOURS,

14:45.350 --> 14:46.751
ISN'T SHE WONDERING
WHY YOU DON'T GET PAID?

14:46.818 --> 14:48.618
OH, SHE THINKS I DO.

14:48.686 --> 14:50.504
I ACTUALLY BORROWED A FEW
THOUSAND DOLLARS FROM MY MOM,

14:50.571 --> 14:54.224
TOLD HER CARRIE NEEDED
A KIDNEY TRANSPLANT.

14:54.292 --> 14:55.325
IT'S ACTUALLY
A PRETTY GOOD LIE, TOO,

14:55.393 --> 14:57.327
'CAUSE SHE PEES A LOT,
YOU KNOW?

14:59.464 --> 15:01.582
HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT,
I NEVER GOT YOUR NAME.

15:01.650 --> 15:03.217
UH, DEACON.
DEACON PALMER.

15:03.285 --> 15:05.702
OH. DOUG HEFFERNAN.

15:05.770 --> 15:09.273
IT'S FUNNY, I'VE NEVER HAD
A BLACK FRIEND BEFORE.

15:09.341 --> 15:12.226
YOU DON'T HAVE ONE NOW.

15:12.293 --> 15:14.061
PALMER.
UH, YES, SIR?

15:14.128 --> 15:16.121
THAT, UH, MR. DAVID'S
BOUTIQUE ON HILLSIDE,

15:16.156 --> 15:18.115
THEY NEVER GOT
THEIR SHIPMENT YESTERDAY.

15:18.183 --> 15:19.483
NOW HIM
AND HIS LIFE PARTNER

15:19.551 --> 15:21.352
ARE THREATENING
TO SCRATCH MY EYES OUT.

15:21.419 --> 15:22.736
RIGHT. WELL, SEE,
WHAT HAPPENED,

15:22.804 --> 15:24.455
I WAS GONNA MAKE THE
DELIVERY, AND I-I GOT-

15:24.522 --> 15:26.907
THAT WAS, UH, MY,
UH, SCREWUP, SIR.

15:26.975 --> 15:28.842
YOURS? WHO ARE YOU?

15:28.910 --> 15:31.195
I'M-I'M DOUG HEFFERNAN.
I'M, UH,

15:31.263 --> 15:32.629
THE NEW DRIVER.

15:32.697 --> 15:34.999
OH, YEAH. RIGHT, RIGHT.

15:35.066 --> 15:36.399
YEAH, UH, I-

15:36.467 --> 15:38.719
I TOLD DEACON I WOULD MAKE
THOSE DELIVERIES, BUT THEN I, UH-

15:38.786 --> 15:40.854
I GOT A PHONE CALL
FROM THE HOSPITAL.

15:40.922 --> 15:44.958
MY UNCLE NEEDED
A KIDNEY TRANSPLANT.

15:45.026 --> 15:46.760
WELL,
WHERE'S YOUR UNIFORM?

15:46.828 --> 15:49.579
I- I GAVE IT
TO MY UNCLE.

15:49.648 --> 15:51.949
GIFT SHOP WAS CLOSED.

15:52.017 --> 15:53.734
WELL, GET ANOTHER ONE.

15:53.802 --> 15:54.902
AND MAKE THAT DELIVERY,
PALMER.

15:54.970 --> 15:56.170
YES, SIR.

15:57.973 --> 16:00.174
THANKS A LOT, MAN.
THAT WAS-THAT WAS NICE.

16:00.242 --> 16:01.608
NO PROBLEM.

16:01.676 --> 16:03.193
YOU, UH-

16:03.261 --> 16:05.996
YOU REALLY LIKE TO WORK THAT
KIDNEY TRANSPLANT THING, DON'T YOU?

16:06.064 --> 16:09.033
IT'S YOUR CADILLAC
OF PERSONAL EMERGENCIES.

16:18.593 --> 16:20.227
HEY,
YOU'RE READING NOW.

16:20.295 --> 16:22.229
WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE SILLY PUTTY?

16:22.297 --> 16:24.331
EH, LOOKIN' FOR A JOB.

16:24.399 --> 16:25.532
OH, YEAH?

16:25.600 --> 16:26.583
YEAH, JUST SOMETHING
TEMPORARY

16:26.651 --> 16:29.819
TILL I GET THE FINANCING
LINED UP FOR MY BREWERY.

16:31.155 --> 16:34.124
LET ME THROW SOMETHING CRAZY
OUT THERE AT YA, BROTHER.

16:34.192 --> 16:35.926
INSTEAD OF JUST HANGING
AROUND HERE EVERY DAY,

16:35.994 --> 16:37.762
WHY DON'T YOU
ACTUALLY WORK HERE?

16:37.829 --> 16:39.530
MMM. YOU KNOW WHAT IT IS?

16:39.598 --> 16:43.066
I'M A CREATIVE BIRD.
I NEED TO FLAP MY WINGS.

16:50.642 --> 16:51.842
HEY!

16:51.909 --> 16:53.877
CARRIE. WH-WHAT
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

16:53.945 --> 16:56.680
SPECIAL DELIVERY
OF HOT LOVIN'.

16:58.182 --> 17:00.467
THAT MEANS KISS ME.
OH. OK.

17:00.535 --> 17:02.869
UH, AREN'T YOU
MISSING WORK?

17:02.937 --> 17:04.888
NAH. THEY'RE DOIN' SOME
STUPID C.P.R. TRAINING.

17:04.955 --> 17:06.123
YAWN.

17:06.190 --> 17:08.291
ANYWAY, I WANTED
TO SURPRISE MY MAN

17:08.358 --> 17:11.028
WITH A LITTLE CARRIE
AND A LITTLE DEBBIE.

17:11.095 --> 17:12.746
THAT'S GREAT. WELL, THANK YOU
SO MUCH. I GOTTA GET GOIN', OK?

17:12.814 --> 17:14.414
HEY, HEFFERNAN, UH,

17:14.482 --> 17:16.233
THERE'S 2 PALLETS
ON A FORKLIFT

17:16.268 --> 17:18.484
THAT SHOULD'VE BEEN
LOADED AN HOUR AGO, HUH?

17:21.372 --> 17:23.140
SO GET ON IT.

17:23.208 --> 17:27.594
DOES THAT MEAN I GET TO
SEE YOU WORK THE FORKLIFT?

17:29.664 --> 17:30.597
I THINK IT DOES.

17:30.665 --> 17:33.400
YAY!

17:41.793 --> 17:43.476
YOU MIGHT WANNA
STAND BACK.

17:43.544 --> 17:45.112
RIGHT, RIGHT.
AHEM.

18:00.745 --> 18:03.447
THIS ONE, SHE'S, UH-
SHE'S, UH, FINICKY.

18:03.515 --> 18:05.315
YOU GOTTA GO BACK
BEFORE YOU GET HER GOIN'.

18:05.383 --> 18:07.101
EVERYBODY COMPLAINS
ABOUT IT.

18:22.050 --> 18:23.284
WE HAD TO OPEN THAT
AND LOOK AT IT.

18:23.351 --> 18:25.585
YOU GOTTA CHECK OUT
THE CONTENTS SOMETIMES.

18:25.653 --> 18:27.637
THIS HAPPENS.

19:03.725 --> 19:06.460
IN MY OFFICE,
NOW!

19:12.767 --> 19:14.567
WONDER WHAT THIS
IS ABOUT.

19:16.471 --> 19:19.807
I GOT ABOUT 250
SMASHED-UP BOXES OUT THERE.

19:19.874 --> 19:21.541
WHAT THE HELL HAPPENED?

19:21.609 --> 19:25.445
I'M NOT REALLY SURE, SIR. SEE, I'M
STILL PRETTY BROKEN UP ABOUT MY UNCLE.

19:25.513 --> 19:27.447
The kidney's not taking.

19:27.515 --> 19:30.601
WELL, FIRST YOU MESS UP THE
DRESS DELIVERY, AND NOW THIS.

19:30.669 --> 19:32.903
I'M SORRY. I GOTTA
LET YOU GO, HEFFERNAN.

19:32.971 --> 19:34.714
SIR, YOU CAN'T DO THAT.
OH, YES, I CAN.

19:34.749 --> 19:36.457
YOU CAN'T, SIR.
I- I DON'T WORK HERE.

19:36.524 --> 19:37.616
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

19:37.651 --> 19:38.709
YOU WERE AT
THE COMPANY PICNIC.

19:38.777 --> 19:41.779
WE WON THE 3-LEGGED RACE
TOGETHER.

19:41.846 --> 19:44.248
I- I DON'T WORK HERE.
I LIED TO MY GIRLFRIEND.

19:44.316 --> 19:45.583
I TOLD HER THIS
IS WHERE I WORKED,

19:45.650 --> 19:46.750
SO FOR THE LAST
COUPLE MONTHS,

19:46.818 --> 19:48.419
I'VE JUST BEEN SHOWING
UP AND HANGING OUT.

19:49.504 --> 19:51.705
OH, FOR CRYING OUT LOUD.

19:53.041 --> 19:54.975
LOOK, BUT IF SHE
- IF SHE KNOWS I BEEN LYING TO HER,

19:55.043 --> 19:56.576
SHE'S GONNA KILL ME,
SO I-

19:56.644 --> 19:58.411
I GUESS WHAT
I'M SAYING IS I-

19:58.479 --> 20:00.747
I'D LIKE TO APPLY
FOR A JOB.

20:02.250 --> 20:06.870
YOU UNDERSTAND, YOU'RE NOT
ASKING AT THE BEST TIME?

20:06.938 --> 20:09.055
I DO UNDERSTAND THAT, SIR,
BUT LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHING,

20:09.123 --> 20:10.223
IF YOU GIVE ME ANOTHER
CHANCE, I'LL SHOW YOU,

20:10.291 --> 20:12.759
I'M THE BEST DAMN DRIVER
YOU'VE EVER SEEN.

20:12.827 --> 20:14.160
WELL...

20:14.228 --> 20:16.162
I'M GONNA BE TOTALLY FRIED
IF CORPORATE FINDS OUT

20:16.230 --> 20:18.632
I LET A CIVILIAN
OPERATE A FORKLIFT.

20:18.700 --> 20:20.567
AND WE ARE DEFENDING
3- LEGGED CHAMPS.

20:20.635 --> 20:22.068
TRUE.

20:23.604 --> 20:25.756
SO, WHAT DO YOU SAY?
CAN I HAVE A JOB?

20:25.824 --> 20:28.325
WELL-

20:28.393 --> 20:32.095
WELL, SINCE I FIRED YOU,
I GUESS THERE'S A SLOT OPEN.

20:33.414 --> 20:35.348
ALL RIGHT,
YOU START ON MONDAY.

20:35.416 --> 20:37.283
ALL RIGHT,
THANKS, SIR.

20:45.693 --> 20:47.060
WANNA SEE MY TRUCK?

20:47.128 --> 20:48.128
YEAH.

20:58.289 --> 21:02.559
<i>COMING UP,
AN ALL-NEW MELROSE PLACE.</i>

21:04.295 --> 21:06.630
<i>I'M EITHER TAKING A BATH
OR WATCHING MELROSE,</i>

21:06.698 --> 21:09.466
OR BOTH! LEAVE A MESSAGE.

21:09.701 --> 21:11.535
HEY, MAN, IT'S DOUG. JUST
WANTED TO LET YOU KNOW

21:11.602 --> 21:14.137
YOU LEFT YOUR JACKET
AT MY HOUSE, AND, UH,

21:14.205 --> 21:15.872
OH, YEAH, KIMBERLY
ISN'T DEAD.

21:15.940 --> 21:18.342
<i>SHE'S ALIVE!
SHE'S ALIVE!</i>

